data.description: New roof, completed Sept. 30, 2023. Charming 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home in Chardonnay Estates. This extremely well maintained home features a family friendly layout with a large kitchen with a gas range, lots of cabinets, pantry,  granite counter tops and a beautiful tile backsplash. A separate office space for those that work remotely and a comfortable gathering area with a gas fireplace. Walk out back to the covered, screened in back porch with your own private hot tub, and a fully fenced back yard (new in 2021). The owners have taken excellent care of this property, new A/C (2021), irrigation pump (2021), home has two hot water heaters, one replaced recently (2020).
